FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1784134075
OL,3,CIran retaliates to third round of US
OL,4,Cstrikes amid fight over Strait of
OL,5,CHormuz
OL,7,FTrump separately suggested the United
OL,8,FStates will charge other ships for
OL,9,Fsafe passage, upending hundreds of
OL,10,Fyears of American policy supporting
OL,11,Ffreedom of navigation across the globe.
OL,13,FHis statement was followed by US
OL,14,Fstrikes on various military sites
OL,15,Ftargets in Iran.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1784134075
OL,3,CIran retaliates to third round of US
OL,4,Cstrikes amid fight over Strait of
OL,5,CHormuz
OL,7,FIran responded with attacks targeting
OL,8,FBahrain, Jordan and two tankers
OL,9,Fassociated with the United Arab
OL,10,FEmirates travelling through the
OL,11,Fstrait, killing one crew on board and
OL,12,Fwounding eight others.
OL,14,FThe Emirates threatened to retaliate
OL,15,Fagainst Iran, potentially drawing the
OL,16,Fnation that is home to Abu Dhabi and
OL,17,FDubai back into fighting with Tehran.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
