PN,31704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1784134075
OL,3,CIran retaliates to third round of US
OL,4,Cstrikes amid fight over Strait of
OL,5,CHormuz
OL,7,FThe attacks come as Iran and the US
OL,8,Fvie for control of the strait through
OL,9,Fwhich a fifth of all traded crude oil
OL,10,Fand natural gas once passed in
OL,11,Fpeacetime.
OL,13,FThe price of a barrel of oil rose to a
OL,14,Fone-month high of over $84 in trading
OL,15,Fearly on Tuesday, still well below the
OL,16,Fnearly $120 reached at the height of
OL,17,Fthe war but threatening to impact
OL,18,Finflation across the globe.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
