PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1784134075
OL,3,CIran retaliates to third round of US
OL,4,Cstrikes amid fight over Strait of
OL,5,CHormuz
OL,7,FThe US military's Central Command said
OL,8,Fit had struck areas around Abu Musa,
OL,9,FBandar Abbas, Bushehr, Chahbahar, Jask
OL,10,Fand Konarak, targeting Iranian
OL,11,F"coastal defence systems, missile and
OL,12,Fdrone sites and maritime capabilities."
OL,14,FIran acknowledged strikes around those
OL,15,Fareas, but provided no immediate
OL,16,Fcasualty or damage assessments.
OL,26,@sD@AOUtD@gO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
