PN,31706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1784134075
OL,3,CIran retaliates to third round of US
OL,4,Cstrikes amid fight over Strait of
OL,5,CHormuz
OL,7,F"These strikes will continue imposing
OL,8,Fa heavy cost on Iranian forces and
OL,9,Fdegrade their ability to attack
OL,10,Finnocent civilians and commercial
OL,11,Fshipping in the Strait of Hormuz," the
OL,12,FUS military said.
OL,14,FMoments after the military announced
OL,15,Fthe new strikes, Trump called it
OL,16,F"another major attack."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@bO]xD@AOUxD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/16
