OL,3,CIran retaliates to third round of US
OL,4,Cstrikes amid fight over Strait of
OL,5,CHormuz
OL,7,F"We're hitting them very hard. And
OL,8,Fit'll continue, and we'll see what
OL,9,Fhappens," he told reporters in the
OL,10,FOval Office. "We're knocking out all
OL,11,Fof their offensive capability and
OL,12,Fwe're controlling the straits. We're
OL,13,Fputting the blockade back."
OL,15,FTrump also provided new details on his
OL,16,Fsuggestion that the US will charge
OL,17,Ftolls for ships going through the
OL,18,Fstrait, an about-face after previously
OL,19,Fsaying that it wouldn't.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@IO]rD@NOUuD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/16
