OL,3,CIran retaliates to third round of US
OL,4,Cstrikes amid fight over Strait of
OL,5,CHormuz
OL,7,F"We're protecting a very rich portion
OL,8,Fof the world," he said. "We're
OL,9,Fspending money. And so, what we've
OL,10,Fdone is, we are going to be reimbursed
OL,11,Ffor protection."
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@NO]pD@YOUsD@PO]
