OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1784134075
OL,3,CIran retaliates to third round of US
OL,4,Cstrikes amid fight over Strait of
OL,5,CHormuz
OL,7,FIt's a change in US policy that, until
OL,8,Fnow, said the strait should remain
OL,9,Fopen to all without tolls, as it was
OL,10,Fbefore the US and Israel attacked Iran
OL,11,Fon February 28. Any attempt by the US
OL,12,For Iran to charge fees would violate
OL,13,Fglobal norms on freedom of navigation
OL,14,Fand raise tensions, likely causing
OL,15,Ffurther economic disruption far beyond
OL,16,Fthe region.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
