OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1784134075
OL,3,CIran retaliates to third round of US
OL,4,Cstrikes amid fight over Strait of
OL,5,CHormuz
OL,7,FThe United Arab Emirates' Defence
OL,8,FMinistry said early on Tuesday that
OL,9,FIran attacked two tankers in the
OL,10,FStrait of Hormuz, killing one mariner
OL,11,Fand wounding eight others.
OL,13,FThe Emirati Defence Ministry said Iran
OL,14,Flaunched two cruise missiles at the
OL,15,Ftankers Mombasa and Al Bahiyah.
OL,17,FThe attacks set both tankers ablaze,
OL,18,Fthough the fires were extinguished.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
