SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1784134075
OL,3,CIran retaliates to third round of US
OL,4,Cstrikes amid fight over Strait of
OL,5,CHormuz
OL,7,FIran's paramilitary Revolutionary
OL,8,FGuard claimed the attack on the
OL,9,Ftankers, saying the vessels "ignored
OL,10,Frepeated warnings."
OL,12,F"They chose to pass through a
OL,13,Fminefield and were subsequently
OL,14,Ftargeted and disabled," the Guard said.
OL,16,FBahrain also came under renewed attack
OL,17,Fearly Tuesday morning as Iran
OL,18,Fretaliated over the latest round of US
OL,19,Fairstrikes.
OL,26,@qD@]OUrD@SO]tD@AOUvD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/16
