OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1784134075
OL,3,CIran retaliates to third round of US
OL,4,Cstrikes amid fight over Strait of
OL,5,CHormuz
OL,7,FBahrain sounded its missile alert
OL,8,Fsirens three times, urging the public
OL,9,Fto seek shelter. There was no word on
OL,10,Fany damage or casualties from the
OL,11,Fattack.
OL,13,FThe Emirati Defence Ministry said the
OL,14,Fattack on the tankers killed one
OL,15,FIndian national and wounded six
OL,16,FIndians and two Ukrainians.
