OL,3,CIran retaliates to third round of US
OL,4,Cstrikes amid fight over Strait of
OL,5,CHormuz
OL,7,F"The UAE reserves its full right to
OL,8,Frespond to this escalation and to take
OL,9,Fall necessary measures to protect its
OL,10,Fterritory, its citizens and
OL,11,Fresidents," the Defence Ministry added.
OL,13,FJordan's military said it intercepted
OL,14,Ffour missiles from Iran, according to
OL,15,Fa statement carried by the kingdom's
OL,16,Fstate-run Petra news agency. Jordan
OL,17,Fhosts US forces and has come under
OL,18,Fattack by Tehran in recent days.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@KO]
