OL,3,CIran retaliates to third round of US
OL,4,Cstrikes amid fight over Strait of
OL,5,CHormuz
OL,7,FEarlier Monday, Trump told
OL,8,Fconservative radio host Hugh Hewitt
OL,9,Fthat the agreement reached last month
OL,10,Fwas "built to test" Iran, adding that
OL,11,F"when you're dealing with sleazebags,
OL,12,Fagreements don't mean much."
OL,14,F"They didn't honour the test," the
OL,15,Fpresident said.
OL,17,FIran asserts it has the right to
OL,18,Fmanage traffic through the strait and
OL,19,Fpotentially charge fees in accordance
OL,20,Fwith the interim peace deal. The US
OL,21,Fhas disputed that.
OL,26,@rD@EOUrD@SO]sD@AOUtD@\O]vD@AOUvD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
