OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1784134075
OL,3,CIran retaliates to third round of US
OL,4,Cstrikes amid fight over Strait of
OL,5,CHormuz
OL,7,FThe American military and the United
OL,8,FNations' International Maritime
OL,9,FOrganisation have tried to establish a
OL,10,Froute through the strait along the
OL,11,Fcoast of Oman that would be outside of
OL,12,FIranian control.
OL,14,FExchanges of fire in recent days had
OL,15,Falready cast further doubt on the
OL,16,Finterim peace deal. Washington had
OL,17,Flifted a blockade it imposed in mid-
OL,18,FApril as part of that deal, which also
OL,19,Fcalled for the strait to be fully
OL,20,Freopened.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31716
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1784134075
OL,3,CIran retaliates to third round of US
OL,4,Cstrikes amid fight over Strait of
OL,5,CHormuz
OL,7,F"We are reinstating the THE IRANIAN
OL,8,FBLOCKADE," Trump said on social media.
OL,9,F"All other countries will have fair
OL,10,Fand open use of the Strait."
OL,12,FThe US military said it will resume
OL,13,Fits blockade of Iranian ports at
OL,14,Fmidnight local time in Dubai on
OL,15,FWednesday.
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@JO]qD@AOUrD@\O]
